{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1679-05_328","@resp":"mercure","head":{"value":"Ambassade du Printemps. Fleurs à Sylvie","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", mai 1679 [tome 5], p. 328-331.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"#1":{"value":"Comme la diversité plaist, &amp; que toutes les Harangues qui ont esté faites au Roy, ne l’ont pas esté en mesme jour, vous trouverez bon que je ne vous parle des autres que dans ma Lettre du premier Mois. Si vostre curiosité en murmure, je vay reparer ce retardement en vous faisant part d’une fort agreable Ambassade. Elle a esté faite au nom du Printemps, qui a député des Fleurs vers une Belle. Vous voyez bien, Madame, que cela sent un Bouquet. Il fut envoyé par M","id":"/div/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" M. à Mademoiselle Fumée le jour de sa Feste. C'est une Personne, belle, spirituelle, &amp; de qualité.","id":"/div/p/#2"}},"quote":{"#":[{"label":[{"@type":"head","#1":{"value":"Ambassade","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label[0]/#1"},"lb":{},"#2":{"value":"du Printemps.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label[0]/#2"}},{"@type":"head","#":{"value":"Fleurs à Sylvie.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label[1]/#"}}]},{"l":[{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[0]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"DU Roy Printemps nous sommes députées,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[0]/#"}},"Pour venir de sa part vous donner le bon jour,","Et pour vous assurer qu’il n’est point en sa Cour","De Fleurs, dont les beautez en tous lieux admirées",{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[4]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[4]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Puissent vous estre comparées.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/l[4]/#"}},{}]},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"l":[{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[0]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[0]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Pour confesser la verité,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[0]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[1]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[1]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Entre les Beautez naturelles,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[1]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[2]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[2]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Je vous le dis sans vanité,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[2]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[3]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[3]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Nous pensions estre les plus belles ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[3]/#"}},{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[4]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"Mais à l’aspect de vos divins apas","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[4]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[5]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[5]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Il nous faut mettre bas les armes,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[5]/#"}},{"seg":{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[6]/seg/#"}},"#":{"value":"Et demeurer d’accord que vous avez des charmes,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[6]/#"}},{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[7]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[7]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Dont les nostres n’approchent pas.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/l[7]/#"}},{}]},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"l":[{"seg":[{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/l[0]/seg[0]/#"}},{"@type":"tab","#":{"value":"    ","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/l[0]/seg[1]/#"}}],"#":{"value":"Les unes devant vous blanchissent,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]